oda-data-set.name: Activated_Devices
oda-data-set.xml-property: select distinct( case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as Approval_status, ( case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as name from device_tag_request d join device_tag_request_ext dt on d.pk=dt.pk union all select '%' as Approval_status ,'SELECT ALL' as name

oda-data-set.name: top_esa_activated
oda-data-set.xml-property: select approval_status,a.company_name as ESA_NAME,a.cbs_acct_code as ESA_CODE,count(*) as Count from( select (case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when (d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null or lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum)='pending' then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as Approval_status, fep.company_name, fep.cbs_acct_code from device_tag_request d left join fep_device_mapping fdm on d.requested_device_id =fdm.device_id left join front_end_partner fep ON fep.pk = fdm.front_end_partner_fk)a where approval_status='ACTIVATED' group by approval_status,company_name,cbs_acct_code order by 4 desc

oda-data-set.name: top_esa_chart
oda-data-set.xml-property: select ESA_NAME,sum(COUNT) as Count,approval_status from( select dt.esa_code,(case when upper(dt.esa_name) like '%LOCA%' then 'NIMC LOCAL PILOT ESA' else upper(dt.esa_name) end)as ESA_NAME ,count(*) as count, (case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as Approval_status from device_tag_request d join device_tag_request_ext dt on d.pk=dt.pk --where rownum <= 10 where upper(dt.esa_name) is not null and upper(dt.esa_name) <> 'NULL' group by upper(dt.esa_name),d.tag_approval_status_enum,dt.esa_code order by count DESC )a group by ESA_NAME,APPROVAL_STATUS ORDER BY Count desc

oda-data-set.name: top_esa_pending_activation
oda-data-set.xml-property: select ESA_NAME,ESA_CODE,approval_status,count(*) as Count from( select dt.esa_code,(case when upper(dt.esa_name) like '%LOCA%' then 'NIMC LOCAL PILOT ESA' else upper(dt.esa_name) end)as ESA_NAME , (case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null or lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum)='pending'then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as Approval_status from device_tag_request d left join device_tag_request_ext dt on d.pk=dt.pk) a where approval_status = 'PENDING ACTIVATION' group by esa_code,esa_name,approval_status order by 4 DESC

oda-data-set.name: total_device_by_status
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(distinct requested_device_id) as Total,approval_status from (select d.requested_device_id,d.tag_approval_status_enum, (case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when (d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null or lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum)='pending' then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as Approval_status from device_tag_request d )a group by approval_status

oda-data-set.name: total_devices
oda-data-set.xml-property: select count(distinct requested_device_id) as total from device_tag_request

oda-data-set.name: whole_dataset
oda-data-set.xml-property: select * from (select dt.agent_email,dt.agent_firstname,dt.agent_lastname,dt.esa_name,dt.agent_phone_number, dt.esa_code,d.requested_device_id, (case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as Approval_status from device_tag_request d join device_tag_request_ext dt on d.pk=dt.pk order by dt.esa_code,dt.esa_name ASC ) a order by approval_status

oda-data-set.name: summary_table
oda-data-set.xml-property: select a.company_name as ESA_NAME,a.cbs_acct_code as ESA_CODE , sum( case when approval_status = 'ACTIVATED' then CNT else 0 end ) total_certified, sum( case when approval_status = 'PENDING ACTIVATION' then CNT else 0 end ) total_pending_activation, sum( case when approval_status = 'DISSAPROVED' then CNT else 0 end ) total_dissaproved, sum(CNT) from( select (case when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='approved' then 'ACTIVATED' when (d.tag_approval_status_enum) is null or lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum)='pending' then 'PENDING ACTIVATION' when lower(d.tag_approval_status_enum) ='disapproved' then 'DISSAPROVED' end) as Approval_status, upper(coalesce(fep.company_name,dte.esa_name)) as company_name, coalesce(fep.cbs_acct_code,dte.esa_code) as cbs_acct_code,1 CNT from device_tag_request d join device_tag_request_ext dte on dte.pk =d.pk left join fep_device_mapping fdm on d.requested_device_id =fdm.device_id left join front_end_partner fep ON fep.pk = fdm.front_end_partner_fk )a --where approval_status='ACTIVATED' group by cbs_acct_code,company_name order by 3 desc
